{"tid":1200284,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"（主內連登家所有巴絲平安）12號唔想沖嘅 參加禱告會 爭取高地 吸引更多和理非到場","createTime":"2019-06-10T17:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T04:52:59.000Z","uid":142348,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd7af4b008151f1a96b0dd6d576a89a151c877b","tid":1200284,"uid":142348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"主內連登家所有巴絲平安！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩條戰線，記得610教訓。<br />\n一少人少記者就會出事。<br />\n一定要多人，而多人最好就係靠和理非，因為大多數都唔想上身。<br />\n<br />\n堅持唔拜神嘅可以去野餐，總之和理非只係記住一件事，多人，做平常野。咁都趕嘅話就更好，引更多人，成個草地仔變做維園草地。<br />\n<br />\n以前以為嘉年華on尻尻，但事實係你冇人，前面咩都唔敢做一盤散沙。<br />\n<br />\nBTW 準備緊三王來朝擺設 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時放係正中間 睇下邊個夠膽郁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n郁親親正惡魔正剎旦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主的家奴<br />\n雙層芝士媽寶"},{"pid":"e6e62eb31deabf62f442778141257a67e0c159a9","tid":1200284,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:16:00.000Z","msg":"到時唔敢衝嘅可以喺人群到帶風向"},{"pid":"796d5611bd71262f459b9510b7cf79bec57a6dc2","tid":1200284,"uid":142348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6e62eb31deabf62f442778141257a67e0c159a9","tid":1200284,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:16:00.000Z","msg":"到時唔敢衝嘅可以喺人群到帶風向"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:17:08.000Z","msg":"示威最緊要多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n610教訓"},{"pid":"ad429710fbac16b42d263aa56d933394046fc153","tid":1200284,"uid":142348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:19:54.000Z","msg":"屌那星 612宗教嘉年華"},{"pid":"4fb4b3b228bd2ba4bd3f35786126ecd6d1f3e931","tid":1200284,"uid":142348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"